A much better statement of your position (and a position that I think everyone here would agree with):<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The problem is that there are wizards who will just get excited by their crits and keep nuking, with little or no regard to aggro.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
